      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：继美国表现最佳后，亚洲股市有望上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/asian-stocks-poised-for-gains-after-best-us-month-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继美国股市周五上涨以及全球市场进入季节性强劲期后，亚洲股市有望谨慎上涨。在美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普进一步发出关税威胁后，发展中国家资产将成为关注焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/asian-stocks-poised-for-gains-after-best-us-month-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 22:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品市场值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球对美国玉米的需求正在攀升。作为全球最大的电线金属供应国，美国的铜产量在连年下滑后正在回升。而中国电动汽车的繁荣有可能削弱汽油需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northern Star 将以 50 亿澳元收购 De Grey Mining 黄金业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/northern-star-to-buy-de-grey-in-deal-valued-at-a-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在贵金属价格飙升的背景下，黄金生产商寻求获得更多供应，Northern Star Resources Ltd. 将以约 50 亿澳元（33 亿美元）的价格收购 De Grey Mining Ltd.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/northern-star-to-buy-de-grey-in-deal-valued-at-a-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 21:36:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
